Notes: Taryn Mellody scores 19 points and pulls down 11 rebounds and tournament
MVP Allison Matt adds 16 points to lead The University of Scranton to a 62-50
victory over DeSales University in Freedom Conference Championship Game;
Jen Netwall scored 24 points--all in 2nd-half--to lead DeSales
Game.Officials: Terry Brazill,  Mike Ognosky,  Jeff Heider
